Name: imasSysUp
Description: Indicates that the iMAS instance is up and active.

Name: imasSysDown
Description: Indicates that the iMAS instance is shutting down.

Name: imasDBConn
Description: Indicates abnormal condition with a database connection pool.

Name: imasHeartBeat
Description: Indicates a heartbeat to inform that the application is running normally.

Name: imasResync
Description: Indicates start and end of traps resync activity.
